name: Baby Fever
overview: When a fertility doctor drunkenly inseminates herself with her ex-boyfriend's sperm, she scrambles to explain her pregnancy — and win back her lost love.

episodes.name: The One That Got Away
episodes.overview: After an unsettling discovery about her discovery to get pregnant, fertility doctor Nana reconnects with an ex and makes an impulsive decision.

episodes.name: What’s Your Big Secret?
episodes.overview: As Nana attempts to manage the fallout from her drunken evening, she starts feeling unwell, prompting her to look into the cause.

episodes.name: You Look Like Someone Who’s About to Throw Up
episodes.overview: To cover up her wrongdoing, Nana hatches a plan that involves wooing Mathias with Greek food. Søren gets a permanent position at the fertility clinic.

episodes.name: Have You Told Him?
episodes.overview: In the wake of a devastating revelation, Nana checks in on Mathias and considers lying to Søren about the father of her baby.

episodes.name: It’s You!
episodes.overview: Nana deals with more consequences of her drunken break-in at the sperm bank. An unexpected visitor causes a stir at the clinic.
